genresAdvancedInfo.name: modern uplift
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre is all about positivity and inspiration. The music is characterized by uplifting melodies, positive lyrics, and catchy hooks that stick in your head. The genre draws on a wide range of influences, from pop and rock to gospel and soul. The songs are designed to make you feel good and motivate you to be your best self. The arrangements are often simple and straightforward, with a focus on the message of the music.
